No. 879. G. A. Rafel & Co., Inc., v. National Labor Relations Board et al. Howard R. Slater for petitioner. Solicitor General Cox, Stuart Rothman, Dominick L. Manoli and Norton J. Come for the National Labor Relations Board, and Bernard M. Mamet for Local No. 9, International Brotherhood of Electrical Workers, AFL-CIO, et al., respondents.

C. A. 7th Cir. Certiorari denied.
